      *
     C           ISYOS     MULT IHAKO     ZOQTY
      *-------*
      * CMD-5 *
      *-------*
     C           *INKE     IFEQ '0'
     C                     GOTO STP3
     C                     END
     C                     GOTO STP5
      *----------*
