     C*                    Z-ADD0         IFSKYY
     C*                    Z-ADD0         IFSKMM
     C*                    Z-ADD0         IFSKDD
     C*                    Z-ADD*DATE     IFKOHZ
     C*                    TIME           IFKOTM
     C*                    MOVELUS        IFKOME
     C*                    Z-ADDIITEM     IFNO
     C*                    Z-ADD0         IFMONT
     C*                    Z-ADD*YEAR     IFYEAR
     C*                    UPDATGDGPL301
